      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is relatively straightforward, involving basic SQL operations such as SELECT and EXECUTE. It does not include complex logic, loops, or conditional branching, which keeps the complexity low."
        }
      ]
    },
